      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation (NIH, wall shear stress distribution) are the same or directly transformable to the decision-relevant QoIs for CPB worst-case identification.",
      "rationale": "NIH and scalar stress exposure time are the primary regulatory QoIs for CPB hemolysis assessment; validation QoIs are identical to decision QoIs. Gradation 2 met."
