      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same device geometry (FDA generic centrifugal pump) and within the CPB operating envelope (2000–3500 RPM, 3–7 L/min).",
      "rationale": "All validation runs used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at CPB-relevant conditions. No geometric surrogates were employed. Gradation 2 satisfied."
