      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood analog fluid properties (viscosity, density) specified with source references; pump geometry sourced from FDA-released CAD.",
      "rationale": "Glycerol-water analog properties from published literature (Brookfield viscometry data). FDA-released STL geometry used without modification. Gradation 1 acceptable at MRL 2."
