      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation boundary conditions shown to be equivalent to experimental conditions within stated measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles extracted from PIV data and applied as CFD boundary conditions. Reynolds number matching confirmed within 2%. Gradation 1 sufficient at MRL 2."
