    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at gradation 1, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2 Class II devices. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB service. Decision: Accepted.",
